public class TestParameters { static {
System . loadLibrary
(
"native"
)
;
}
public native long
sumIntegers (
int
first
,
int
second
)
;
public native String
sayHelloToMe (
String
name
,
boolean
isFemale
)
;
public static void
main (
String []
args
)
{
TestParameters
instance =
new
TestParameters ()
;
String
name =
"John"
;
boolean
isFemale =
false
;
String
hello =
instance . sayHelloToMe
(
name
,
isFemale
)
;
System . out . println
(
"Java: My full name: "
+ hello
)
;
int
val1 =
456
;
int
val2 =
44
;
long
sumFromNative =
instance . sumIntegers
(
val1
,
val2
)
;
System . out . println
(
"Java: The sum coming from native code is: "
+ sumFromNative
)
;
}
}
